        public void onBacktrack(MatchingFrame frame,
                        ISearchContext context)
        Description copied from interface: ISearchOperation
        After the execution of the operation failed and ISearchOperation.execute(MatchingFrame, ISearchContext) returns false, the onBacktrack callback is evaluated. Operations may use this method to clean up any temporary structures, and make the operation ready for a new execution.
